            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro salute et reditu <lb n="2"/>et victorias <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>dom</abbr><ex>ini</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aureli Anto<lb break="no" n="4"/>nini Pii <expan><abbr>Fel</abbr><ex>icis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Brit</abbr><ex>annici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>et Iuliae <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mat</abbr><ex>ris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> et <lb n="6"/>castrorum <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Valerio Dato <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aefecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>vig</abbr><ex>ilum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>gregio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> et <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> Aelio Anniano <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ub</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aefecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Ulpio <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschrift für Caracalla aus der Collezione Muñoz; unten abgebrochen, links stark bestoßen. Herkunft nach Barbieri unbekannt; nach G. Alföldy entweder aus Rom oder vielleicht aus Ostia (CIL 06, 40647). Autopsie G. Alföldy. Die Inschrift ist nach Getas Tod gesetzt, jedoch vor Ende September 213, d.h. vor der Annahme des Siegertitels Germanicus maximus.</p>
            </div>
